                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9057" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0115</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1891 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字缘起,变革涅槃:HMC 公司组织变革之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Origins, Nirvana of Change: The Way of Organizational Change in HMC Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山红梅，孙艺杰，韩红霞，成育红，史文婷，马俊程，周胜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西宏铭城建材有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；组织变革；扁平化组织；平台型组织；</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation; organisational change; flat organisation; platform organisation;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着新一代数字技术蓬勃发展并深入经济社会等各个领域，数字化转型成为建材企业摆脱传统经济增长方式，加快构建并形成新质生产力的重要引擎。本案例以HMC公司的数字化转型为背景，描述了HMC公司在面对传统组织结构与数字化转型战略不合拍现象时，审时度势、谋求变革、持续改革组织结构的过程。为适应市场需求的变化，HMC公司将原有的金字塔型组织结构转变为扁平化组织结构，来提高组织效率、实现信息活跃；随后，又将扁平化组织结构进一步转变为平台型组织结构，来更好地适应数字转型的进程。本案例旨在引导学生学习在数字化转型背景下，HMC公司组织结构变革的历程和变革中的阻力以及解决措施等关键实施路径，并进一步分析和讨论平台型组织的特点，有助于培养学生适应新时代经济技术发展趋势，提高学生理论结合实际分析与解决实际问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the new generation of digital technology develops vigorously and penetrates into various fields of economy and society, digital transformation has become an important engine for building materials enterprises to get rid of the traditional economic growth mode and accelerate the construction and formation of new quality productivity. This case takes the digital transformation of HMC Company as the background, describing the process of HMC Company in the face of the phenomenon that the traditional organisational structure and the digital transformation strategy do not match, assessing the situation, seeking change, and continuously reforming the organisational structure. In order to adapt to the changes in market demand, HMC transformed the original pyramid-type organisational structure into a flat organisational structure to improve organisational efficiency and realise information activation; subsequently, it further transformed the flat organisational structure into a platform-type organisational structure to better adapt to the process of digital transformation. This case aims to guide students to learn the course of organisational change of HMC under the background of digital transformation and the key implementation paths such as resistance and solution measures, and further analyse and discuss the characteristics of platform-type organisation, which helps to cultivate students&#39; ability to adapt to the development trend of the economy and technology in the new era, and to improve their ability of analysing and solving practical problems by combining theory with practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；组织变革；组织变革的内涵与过程；组织变革的阻力及措施；扁平化组织和平台型组织的搭建方式；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
